<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-39-0200 </DOCNO><TEXT>To improve the accuracy of diagnosis a method of diagnosis of immunocomplexpulmonary lesions is proposed. The method lies in the following: afterroentgenography of the lungs prednisolone is injected during a week andthen roentgenography of the lungs is repeated, and when the pulmonarypattern has changed to normalization, the diagnosis of immunocomplexpulmonary lesions is stated. An illustration is given how to use theproposed method of diagnosis decreasing the diagnosis time twice andimproving the accuracy of diagnosis.</TEXT></DOC>